description:
This is a 20 minute workout called 'Full Body Total Beginner Workout' from the channel growwithjo.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Comfort Moves vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Jumpstart your fitness journey with this full-body workout designed specifically for total beginners! Get ready to boost your confidence and build a solid foundation with easy-to-follow moves that work every major muscle group. Perfect for anyone new to exercise, this workout will help improve strength, flexibility, and endurance without the need for equipment. Start today and feel empowered to reach your fitness goals one step at a time!
